front.desc:
//"I don't know, I just felt ... something ... flow through me!" -- Tana
The mystical, the eldritch, the arcane. The Power has many names. When called, it always comes. That doesn't mean you can always command it.
Magic lets you achieve a variety of supernatural outcomes, with costs and consequences that sometimes don't make rational sense.

